<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <title>Password Reset - Hamsoya</title>
    <style>
      /* Same styles as OTP verification */
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto,
          Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333333;
        background-color: #ececec;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        width: 100% !important;
        min-width: 100%;
        -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
        -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;
      }

      table {
        border-collapse: collapse;
        mso-table-lspace: 0pt;
        mso-table-rspace: 0pt;
      }

      img {
        border: 0;
        height: auto;
        line-height: 100%;
        outline: none;
        text-decoration: none;
        -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic;
      }

      .email-container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ececec;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .background-layer {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        z-index: 1;
      }

      .gradient-primary {
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ff6925 0%, #fff 46.48%);
        filter: blur(50px);
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        z-index: 2;
      }

      .gradient-secondary {
        background: linear-gradient(
          180deg,
          #4d5de9 11.31%,
          rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) 46.48%
        );
        filter: blur(50px);
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        z-index: 3;
      }

      .content-wrapper {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 10;
        padding: 40px 20px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        margin: 60px 20px;
        border-radius: 16px;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }

      .header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
      }

      .logo {
        font-size: 32px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #4d5de9;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .tagline {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #666666;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }

      .main-title {
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #333333;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        line-height: 1.3;
      }

      .subtitle {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #666666;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }

      .otp-container {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6925 0%, #4d5de9 100%);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 30px;
        text-align: center;
        margin: 40px 0;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(255, 105, 37, 0.3);
      }

      .otp-label {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .otp-code {
        font-size: 36px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #ffffff;
        letter-spacing: 8px;
        font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      }

      .otp-expiry {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
        font-weight: 500;
      }

      .instructions {
        background: #f8f9fa;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 24px;
        margin: 30px 0;
        border-left: 4px solid #ff6925;
      }

      .instructions h3 {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #333333;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .instructions ol {
        margin: 0;
        padding-left: 20px;
        color: #555555;
      }

      .instructions li {
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }

      .security-notice {
        background: #fff3cd;
        border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 16px;
        margin: 30px 0;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .security-notice .icon {
        font-size: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }

      .security-notice p {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #856404;
        margin: 0;
        line-height: 1.4;
      }

      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 40px;
        padding-top: 30px;
        border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
      }

      .footer p {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #888888;
        margin: 8px 0;
        line-height: 1.4;
      }

      .footer a {
        color: #4d5de9;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .footer a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
        .email-container {
          width: 100% !important;
          max-width: 100% !important;
        }

        .content-wrapper {
          margin: 20px 10px !important;
          padding: 30px 16px !important;
          border-radius: 12px !important;
        }

        .main-title {
          font-size: 24px !important;
        }

        .otp-code {
          font-size: 28px !important;
          letter-spacing: 4px !important;
        }

        .otp-container {
          padding: 24px 16px !important;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-container">
      <div class="background-layer">
        <div class="gradient-primary"></div>
        <div class="gradient-secondary"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="content-wrapper">
        <div class="header">
          <div class="logo">Hamsoya</div>
          <div class="tagline">Your trusted marketplace</div>
        </div>

        <h1 class="main-title">Reset Your Password</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">
          Hi <%= name %>,<br />
          We received a request to reset your password for your Hamsoya account. 
          Use the verification code below to reset your password.
        </p>

        <div class="otp-container">
          <div class="otp-label">Password Reset Code</div>
          <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>
          <div class="otp-expiry">This code expires in 5 minutes</div>
        </div>

        <div class="instructions">
          <h3>How to reset your password:</h3>
          <ol>
            <li>Copy the verification code above</li>
            <li>Return to the password reset page</li>
            <li>Enter the code and your new password</li>
            <li>Click "Reset Password" to complete the process</li>
          </ol>
        </div>

        <div class="security-notice">
          <div class="icon">ðŸ”’</div>
          <p>
            <strong>Security Notice:</strong> If you didn't request this password reset, 
            please ignore this email. Your account remains secure.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
          <p>This email was sent because a password reset was requested for your Hamsoya account.</p>
          <p>
            If you have any questions, please contact us at
            <a href="mailto:support@hamsoya.com">support@hamsoya.com</a>
          </p>
          <p>
            Â© 2024 Hamsoya. All rights reserved.<br />
            <a href="#">Privacy Policy</a> | <a href="#">Terms of Service</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
